    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "Discussion",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Use this method in conjunction with a custom overlay view to initiate the programmatic capture of a still image. This supports taking more than one picture without leaving the interface, but requires that you hide the default image picker controls.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Calling this method while an image is being captured has no effect. You must wait until the associated delegate object receives an ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.uikit/documentation/UIKit/UIImagePickerControllerDelegate/imagePickerController(_:didFinishPickingMediaWithInfo:)",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " message before you can capture another picture.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "Calling this method when the source type of the image picker is set to a value other than ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.uikit/documentation/UIKit/UIImagePickerController/SourceType-swift.enum/camera",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " results in the throwing of an ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.documentation/documentation/foundation/nsexceptionname/1415426-invalidargumentexception",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " exception.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
